            </div>

            </div>
        
        
        <div type="footnotes">
            <note xml:id="foot.f1">The year is established by the relationship between this letter and the <ref target="./DCP-LETT-13039.xml">letter from W. E. Darwin, 6 February 1881</ref>.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-13039.xml">letter from W. E. Darwin, 6 February 1881</ref> and n. 1.</note>
