            <note xml:id="foot.f4"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1240.xml">Sara Darwin</ref>, William’s wife.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f5">A scathing review by <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1262.xml">William Boyd Dawkins</ref> of <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1837.xml">James Geikie</ref>’s <hi rend="italic">Prehistoric Europe: a geological sketch</hi> (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_9520.xml">J. Geikie 1881</ref>) was published in <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi>, 3 February 1881, pp. 309–10. A reply from Geikie appeared in <hi rend="italic">Nature</hi>, 10 February 1881, p. 336.</note>
